{"tid":634492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你覺得愛情應該係點？","createTime":"2018-04-19T09:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:33:27.000Z","uid":41176,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1a2d1db4ff8fb3652ae8858338b2f03b84dc6f","tid":634492,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"愛一個人，應該係愛佢所擁有嘅價值(例如：細心，溫柔等等)定係愛個人本身呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果係愛佢嘅價值，個人本身就只會變成個價值嘅載體，當佢冇咗呢啲價值嘅時候就會有所謂嘅感情淡咗然後就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係愛佢個人本身，就係無視佢嘅所承載嘅價值有咩變化，佢變成點都好，你係因為佢係佢所以愛，似係一種無條件嘅愛。但係可能最後會咩回報都得唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛佢嘅價值，鍾意一個人係鍾意佢嘅內涵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛係應該冇條件，因為佢係佢所以愛"},{"pid":"0ceb73e8eae0cf00977b2f0aecf08ba72a4401a0","tid":634492,"uid":2263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"因世上的至愛 是不計較條件"},{"pid":"c86698845312d0bcc3beba26e66cf54cb26ac986","tid":634492,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"真愛係不計較付出 不計較條件<br />\n無論佢變成點，你都係愛佢"},{"pid":"eac188a35fdfce8b710b7024363d1216c5fe4ebb","tid":634492,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f72ea734f6698690cf11423820552d5e2925d93","tid":634492,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係睇中個個人既價值，那你只係睇中佢外表"},{"pid":"68514af5e1cbf58d4dfbd0fc2749b1b00d6f6ab3","tid":634492,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"我都係覺得應該唔計條件<br />\n但係如果你愛嘅人對你懶咗開始冇記性<br />\n你哋會唔會覺得好辛苦？<br />\n愛情如果淨係愛佢而唔愛自己會唔會行得長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d496597ecd3361b9908573fbbacc1f1d489568","tid":634492,"uid":41176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f72ea734f6698690cf11423820552d5e2925d93","tid":634492,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係睇中個個人既價值，那你只係睇中佢外表"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"咁又唔一定嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時荷爾蒙嘅嘢真係話唔埋<br />\n有時嗰個人係靚係醜都好，仲有一個人令你死心塌地嘅"},{"pid":"30218bef669965ffeda75e6f5eb81062ce9ce2b9","tid":634492,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"Both"},{"pid":"2b109dcf3b68e547e85b31a5d92e421e0d59ae82","tid":634492,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30218bef669965ffeda75e6f5eb81062ce9ce2b9","tid":634492,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"Both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"點解咁講呢巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91abb05d1fba1ad081074bbfbf381719c5aa150","tid":634492,"uid":36692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得無條件的愛只會係老豆老母道黎.<br />\n世間千千萬萬個人,<br />\n你揀中果個一定有原因.<br />\n個原因咪你心入面的價值."},{"pid":"94764bc65f5d6c76dbe98c22efc0b0f31d9e4922","tid":634492,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b109dcf3b68e547e85b31a5d92e421e0d59ae82","tid":634492,"uid":41176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30218bef669965ffeda75e6f5eb81062ce9ce2b9","tid":634492,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"Both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"點解咁講呢巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"兩樣夾埋先係個人"}]}